Body:
Description: Kindly provide us with the latest upgrade patch for our EPP server. We are currently running 5.9.1.0. 
Also we would like to acquire some offline documentations for EPP, as well as the SLA details for our account; These are required by our internal audit team.
Steps to Reproduce Updated: Documentation + server upgrade
What We've Learned Updated: The customer needed guidance on how to perform server upgrade
Next Steps Updated: deliver the requested informations
